{"tid":1626344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"目標係成個星期三罷","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:36:25.000Z","uid":132999,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed71e83d1d71e18d09a48fbb0830c9a7f4a55b6","tid":1626344,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"尋日基本上下晝已經大部分公司收皮，今日死鐵死商場同大量商店，事實上已經係罷咗日半市。<br />\n<br />\n政府揀得喺長假前出緊急法，就係希望用一個長假嘅時間令件事開始淡，而令到下星期成個城市運作開始正常，所以我哋一定要自己罷工加幫人罷工，用行動話俾個政府聽緊急法唔 ok。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"3fb5026d69ff0d37be07201d9d9db247497952dd","tid":1626344,"uid":132999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"674ab0962f4949971914bb203af93d9086362df5","tid":1626344,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:59:00.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"8f624f78b7145c8a93279e9ed0dc69914404c1b0","tid":1626344,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:59:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"},{"pid":"821b174847eab96ae10755164c44ac8cd860bb18","tid":1626344,"uid":126062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日十月八 全民三罷 全港繼續死城 </span></span></strong><br />\n有冇人跟！！有既急需文宣！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634432/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ebd94d29de51fa2ef86a8d4865fb1d4728891bec","tid":1626344,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:05:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新口號：和勇相連 絕不割蓆！</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和勇相連 決不分割<br />\n和勇相連 不分不割<br />\n和勇相連 永不分割<br />\n和勇相連 勢不分割"},{"pid":"26b8e1545e1fc9f4c95b3cd24ba98f88fc5022bd","tid":1626344,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"今晚千期唔好拆鐵<br />\n聽朝千期唔好塞路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c2d0f3c5de13b1008c1bdfb77ddbc0d7f0368e","tid":1626344,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"緊急法下份勞工保險無效。聽朝返工？不了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11c23bf1109f459021c86ef4506933305f4e5184","tid":1626344,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"d0fa5fd561a015cc5e791114d0e02568c79c8936","tid":1626344,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c2d0f3c5de13b1008c1bdfb77ddbc0d7f0368e","tid":1626344,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"緊急法下份勞工保險無效。聽朝返工？不了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"政府出聲明從來無回應過保險問題"},{"pid":"34e170814ae77ad3795fa30d80acfbc5a5681289","tid":1626344,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0fa5fd561a015cc5e791114d0e02568c79c8936","tid":1626344,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c2d0f3c5de13b1008c1bdfb77ddbc0d7f0368e","tid":1626344,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"緊急法下份勞工保險無效。聽朝返工？不了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"政府出聲明從來無回應過保險問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:36:25.000Z","msg":"即係void左，連保險公司都唔declare"}]}